      "layout": "The page primarily uses a max-width contained layout, though the hero section is full-bleed with a centered headline over a dark background. Sections alternate between light and dark themes, creating distinct visual blocks. Content is often arranged in symmetrical stacks or two-column layouts with text and visuals balanced. Card grids are used for features, showcasing clear divisions between items. Overall density is comfortable, ensuring sufficient negative space.",
